rComments: Guest speakers were awesome, field trip to a Zen Buddhist temple was fun. One midterm, one paper worth 50% and no final exam. All information is on her slides. Pretty much a more in-depth repeat of NEW232. Fun class though, and if you're good at writing essays, you'll be fine.

Awesome course. Had a trip to Zen Temple. Paper on that. Then a test and another paper worth 50%. Pretty straightforward and easy to get A if you attend and pay attention. No textbook but she does send notes online. Guest lecs too. She should speak louder. Overall interesting stories & useful for life. :)
